{"tid":2107920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［保就業］國泰獲批4.5億 新鴻基啟勝管理獲批1.36億 民建聯獲批754萬","createTime":"2020-07-14T07:50:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T10:30:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"4bad8fce10206fdc9f4bd53102724eb68a0647f3","tid":2107920,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:50:42.000Z","msg":"第四批名單當中，早前獲得政府動用土地基金出手拯救的國泰航空（0293）獲批最多補助金，呈報僱員人數 17,703 人，獲批金額 4.58 億，是計劃推出以來獲得最多補貼額的機構。至於排第二是九巴，呈報僱員人數 12,590 人，獲批金額 3.24 億。至於排第三的是新鴻基地產旗下的「啟勝管理服務有限公司」，呈報僱員人數 5,780 人，獲批金額 1.36 億。受到疫情影響需要兩度關閉的海洋公園，呈報僱員人數 2,891 人，獲批金額 5,967 萬。建制派政黨民建聯亦有申請計劃，呈報僱員人數 305 人，獲批 754 萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BF%9D%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E7%8D%B2%E8%BF%91-4-6-%E5%84%84-%E4%B9%9D%E5%B7%B4-3-2-%E5%84%84-%E6%B0%91%E5%BB%BA%E8%81%AF%E9%83%BD%E6%9C%89-754-%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25BF%2591-4-6-%25E5%2584%2584-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4-3-2-%25E5%2584%2584-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2589-754-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%2F&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCnz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=1f11d484\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E7%258D%25B2%25E8%25BF%2591-4-6-%25E5%2584%2584-%25E4%25B9%259D%25E5%25B7%25B4-3-2-%25E5%2584%2584-%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%2581%25AF%25E9%2583%25BD%25E6%259C%2589-754-%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%2F&h=9b203c9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%BF%9D%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E7%8D%B2%E8%BF%91-4-6-%E5%84%84-%E4%B